\c 39
\s Munyengetero pakutambudzika
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba, kuna Jedhutuni. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Ndakati, "Ndichachenjerera nzira dzangu, Kuti ndirege kutadza norurimi rwangu; Ndichachengeta muromo wangu netomu, Kana wakaipa ari pamberi pangu."
\v 2 Ndakanga ndiri mbeveve ndisingatauri, Ndakanyarara hangu, ndiri kure nezvakanaka. Kuchema kwangu kukamutswa.
\v 3 Mwoyo wangu wakanga uchipisa mukati mangu; Ndakati ndichifunga, moto ukapfuta; Ipapo ndakataura norurimi rwangu, ndikati,
\v 4 "Jehovha, ndizivisei mugumo wangu, Uye mwero wamazuva angu, kuti akadini; Ndizivisei kuti ndinongopfuura hangu."
\v 5 Tarirai, makaita mazuva angu sohupamhi hwechanza; Uye ng,uva yokurarama kwai-kgu sechinhu chisipo pamberi penyu; Zvirokwazvo, munhu mumwe nomumwe kunyange akasimba kwazvo, mweya bedzi.
\v 6 Zvirokwazvo, munhu mumwe nomumwe anofamba-famba somumvuri; Zvirokwazvo, vanoita hope pasina; Anounganidza pfuma, asi haazivi kuti ndiani achaidya.
\v 7 Zvino Ishe, ndakarindireiko? Tariro yangu iri kwamuri.
\v 8 Ndirwirei pakudarika kwangu kwose; Regai kundiita munhu anosekwa namapenzi.
\v 9 Ndakanga ndiri mbeveve, handina kushamisa muromo wangu; Nokuti ndimi makazviita.
\p
\v 1 ° Bvisai shamhu yenyu kwandiri;
\s Ndapera nokurohwa noruoko
\s rwenyu.
\s IlKana muchiraira munhu muchimuranga
\s pamusoro pezvakaipa,
\s Munopedza kunaka kwake sechiunduzi;
\s Zvirokwazvo munhu mumwe
\s nomumwe mweya hake.
\p
\v 12 Inzwai munyengetero wangu, Jehovha,
\s rerekerai nzeve yenyu
\s munzwe kuchema kwangu; Musanyarara muchiona misodzi yangu;
\s Nokuti ndiri mweni kwamuri, Mutorwa, sezvakanga zvakaita madzibaba angu ose.
\p
\v 13 Regai kunditarira,
\s kuti ndimbonaya hangu,
\s Ndisati ndabva pano,
\s ndikasazovapo.
\p
\v 6 Zvirokwazvo, munhu mumwe nomumwe
\s anofamba-famba somumvuri; Zvirokwazvo, vanoita hope pasina; Anounganidza pfuma, asi haazivi kuti ndiani achaidya.
\s Zvino Ishe, ndakarindireiko? Tariro yangu iri kwamuri.
\p
\v 8 Ndirwirei pakudarika kwangu kwose;
\s Regai kundiita munhu anosekwa namapenzi.
\p
\v 9 Ndakanga ndiri mbeveve, handina kushamisa muromo wangu; Nokuti ndimi makazviita.
